OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FReform UK says it has no plans to
OL,7,Finvestigate its candidate for the
OL,8,FMakerfield by-election, after
OL,9,Fallegations a social media account
OL,10,Flinked to him contained offensive
OL,11,Fposts.
OL,13,FSocial media posts from a now-deleted
OL,14,FX account associated with Robert
OL,15,FKenyon have been uncovered, showing
OL,16,Fsexist, violent and homophobic
OL,17,Fmessages.
OL,19,FA spokesperson from Reform UK said:
OL,20,F"We fully back Cllr Kenyon."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
