OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FThe statement added that the comments
OL,7,Fwere made "before he entered politics".
OL,9,FThe posts include conspiracy theories
OL,10,Faround the Covid-19 pandemic, lewd
OL,11,Fcomments about presenter Carol
OL,12,FVorderman and offensive sexual
OL,13,Fcomments about female rugby players.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
