OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FDuring the pandemic, Kenyon suggested
OL,7,Fsome media outlets "were complicit" in
OL,8,F"global tyranny" in response to a post
OL,9,Fby far-right influencer Peter Sweden,
OL,10,Fwho has a history of Holocaust denial.
OL,12,FKenyon also compared Australia's Covid
OL,13,Fvaccination to Nazism and called for
OL,14,FRichard Branson, along with other
OL,15,Fbusinessmen, to be hanged for
OL,16,Faccepting furlough payments to pay
OL,17,Ftheir workers in lockdown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
