PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FHe posted about climate change
OL,7,Fclaiming it is "a middle class issue"
OL,8,Fand said schools are "teaching about
OL,9,Fthe ice age and that the world has
OL,10,Fbeen getting warmer since then".
OL,12,FHe also replied to a post about the
OL,13,FLabour party using a transphobic slur.
OL,15,FReform UK said: "These comments were
OL,16,Fmade before he was in politics. Rob
OL,17,Fisn't a polished, professional
OL,18,Fpolitician and doesn't speak like one.
OL,19,FThat's precisely why he'll be a
OL,20,Fstraight-talking, effective voice for
OL,21,Fnormal working people in Makerfield."
OL,26,@wD@QOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
