OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FIn a message of support for its
OL,7,Fcandidate, Reform UK explained that
OL,8,Finteracting with figures on social
OL,9,Fmedia does not mean that Kenyon
OL,10,Fendorses or shares the same views.
OL,12,FAnti-facist campaign group Searchlight
OL,13,Falso claimed that Kenyon was Facebook
OL,14,Ffriends with three far-right
OL,15,Forganisers on a now-deleted page,
OL,16,Fincluding fascist campaigner Gary
OL,17,FRaikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
