PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FReform UK has denied this connection,
OL,7,Fsaying he had never "spoken or engaged
OL,8,Fwith" Gary Raikes and that when he was
OL,9,Fmade aware of who Raikes was, Kenyon
OL,10,F"removed him from his Facebook
OL,11,Fimmediately".
OL,13,FThe party is also facing questions
OL,14,Fabout another X account, owned by
OL,15,FKenyon, which was terminated by the
OL,16,Fsocial media company in 2024.
OL,18,FOn Friday, Nigel Farage shared a
OL,19,Fnearly 10 minute campaign video of
OL,20,Fhimself and Robert Kenyon talking
OL,21,Fabout his background.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
