OL,3,CReform UK backs by-election candidate
OL,4,Caccused of posting offensive comments
OL,6,FCandidates for the Makerfield by-
OL,7,Felection have until Tuesday, May 26 to
OL,8,Fdeclare.
OL,10,FThe current list of candidates is:
OL,12,FLiberal Democrats - Jake Austin
OL,14,FLabour - Andy Burnham
OL,16,FMonster Raving Loony Party - Alan
OL,17,F'Howlin' Laud Hope
OL,19,FRestore Britain - Rebecca Shepherd
OL,21,FConservatives - Michael Winstanley
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
